name: WEREWOLF DYST02
description:
The Beast captured at midnight on METALPOLIS, looking for a weak prey for dinner. WEREWOLF DYST02 is a teenage mutant, human name; Lyco from lykánthropos (λυκάνθρωπος). Has a friendly side at daytime and gory side at night, you choose.

p.s: Those glasses help him to quickly find fresh meat

-Cyberartlab
